---
title: Sheet Pan Tilapia Tacos with DIY Baja Sauce
description: Enjoy family-friendly fish tacos without the fuss of frying! This simple sheet pan supper makes weeknight meals a breeze. Corn and peppers roast alongside Tex-Mex spiced tilapia. Everyone in the family can load up their tacos as they'd like with DIY Baja sauce, veggies, lime and flakes of tender fish.

